When every submission must succeed and order matters — such as recording each ball's runs in sequence — use `enqueue`. `drop` would silently discard submissions that arrive while a fetch is in-flight, causing data loss. `enqueue` serializes all calls and processes them in the order received, with `numQueued` available for a progress indicator.

