```

This form demonstrates the full submit task pattern: computed `isValid` getter validates synchronously without any task, `canSubmit` combines validation with `isRunning` to control button state, and `drop` prevents double submission. The success state replaces the form entirely to give clear completion feedback. Error messages come from the server's JSON body when available.

