The `enqueue` policy ensures load-more clicks don't create overlapping fetches — each request waits for the previous to complete before firing. Pages are accumulated via spread into `@tracked fixtures`. A progress bar shows load percentage. The "remaining" count helps users know how much more content exists before deciding to continue scrolling.

