The `drop` policy prevents duplicate exports from double clicks. The download is triggered programmatically using a temporary `<a>` element with `download` attribute and `click()` — the browser handles the save dialog. `URL.revokeObjectURL` immediately after click frees memory since the browser has already queued the download. Format selection uses a simple `@tracked selectedFormat` string rather than a task.

