  </div>
</template>
```

The auction component tracks budget, current bid, and bid history as separate `@tracked` properties. `BID_INCREMENTS` provides preset bid jump buttons. The `canBid` getter guards against over-budget bids, won status, and in-flight requests. When the server returns `won` status, the budget is decremented and the won-player state is shown. The `drop` policy prevents simultaneous bid submissions from rapid taps.

