Optimistic UI is applied in `markAchieved` — the milestone is immediately toggled locally before the API call. If `saveMilestone` fails, the milestone is rolled back to `achieved: false`. The `achievedCount` getter reactively updates as milestones change. Multiple milestones can be saved concurrently since `saveMilestone` is not `drop`.

