The `restartable` task cancels any in-flight search when a new keystroke arrives, preventing stale results from overwriting fresh ones. A 300ms `timeout()` debounce reduces unnecessary API calls. The `highlightText` method safely escapes regex special characters before wrapping matches in a yellow `<mark>` tag styled with Tailwind.

