The `assignments` object is replaced immutably on every change to trigger Glimmer reactivity. The `unassignedPlayers` getter filters out already-assigned players, though all players are shown in each dropdown for flexibility. The save button only enables when all positions are filled. The `drop` modifier prevents saving twice while one save is in progress.

