The `overRate` getter is computed fresh each render from `currentOver` and `elapsedMinutes`, which are updated every 10 seconds by the polling task. `isSlowAlert` is set inside the task after the getter value is recalculated. The monitor task is cleaned up in `willDestroy` to avoid polling after the component unmounts.

