The carousel only starts after logos are loaded, preventing empty rotations. The `carouselTask` uses an infinite loop with `timeout()` to advance `activeIndex` using modulo arithmetic so it wraps back to 0 after the last logo. The interval is configurable via `@args.intervalMs`. Both tasks are cleaned up in `willDestroy` to stop the loop when the component is removed.

