    </div>
  </template>
}
```

The `restartable` modifier cancels any pending save when a new keystroke arrives, implementing debouncing without a manual `clearTimeout`. The 800ms `timeout()` ensures the API is only called after the user pauses typing. `saveStatus` cycles through `idle → saving → saved/error`, driving the status indicator text and color. Notes are pre-loaded on mount so the editor is never blank on return visits.

