Every field change pushes the current state onto `undoStack` and clears `redoStack` (standard undo/redo semantics). Undo pops from `undoStack` and pushes to `redoStack`; redo does the reverse. `isDirty` uses JSON comparison between current state and last saved state. The save button disables when there are no unsaved changes, preventing unnecessary API calls.

